  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes [INAUDIBLE] say, although, historically they could be killed for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But here you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was a well-kept secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was completely unique in history, it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, under those conditions, horrible conditions-- and I'm not going into much of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That alone is so much suffering that it's unbelievable to see how many people died in the ghetto of starvation, of illnesses, and the suffering of the little children and the old people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many times.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many times my parents would take and-- and I myself-- I would give to my little sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we thought, they're younger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while the grandmother was alive, we always protected the grandmother first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But unfortunately she-- unfortunately and fortunately, she died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, on November-- the night of November 17, 1942, the Nazis told us we're going to be resettled to a better place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we going or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us this time a little more bread, and we were so happy [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, maybe there is actually going to be a turnaround.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, and we went-- they put us aboard the train, put us in hermetically sealed cattle trains, packed us in like sardines without food in the trains, just what we got for the ration.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No facilities to relieve ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the train already when we came-- we traveled from November 17.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we arrived to Auschwitz-Birkenau it was November 22nd.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
